<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <link rel="icon" href="img/logo.jpg">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/FAQ.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta2/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/loader.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">
            Frequenty Asked Questions
        </h1>
        <main class="accordion">
            <div class="faq-img">
                <img src="img/faq.png" alt="" class="accordion-img">
            </div>
            <div class="content-accordion">
                <div class="question-answer">
                    <div class="question">
                        <h3 class="title-question">
                            What is the main motive for this website?
                        </h3>
                        <button class="question-btn">
                            <span class="up-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="down-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>Students get a platform to showcase their talent.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question-answer">
                    <div class="question">
                        <h3 class="title-question">
                            What is the future for our website?
                        </h3>
                        <button class="question-btn">
                            <span class="up-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="down-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>Companies will be able to access the work done by the students directly over here.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question-answer">
                    <div class="question">
                        <h3 class="title-question">
                            Is this website user-friendly for viewers?
                        </h3>
                        <button class="question-btn">
                            <span class="up-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="down-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>Yes the website has a very user friendly layout and is a lot helpful for students to revisit and access their projects.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question-answer">
                    <div class="question">
                        <h3 class="title-question">
                            Is the information of the students who have done the project available here?
                        </h3>
                        <button class="question-btn">
                            <span class="up-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="down-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>No, the students details will not be given directly they will be addressed with their group no. and the institute name.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question-answer">
                    <div class="question">
                        <h3 class="title-question">
                            Are there any charges for the process of project upload?
                        </h3>
                        <button class="question-btn">
                            <span class="up-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="down-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>No, as the website is specially designed for university students we donâ€™t have any charges applicable for project uploading. The students will be guided to upload the project on the website after guidance from the concerned faculty of their university.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
    <script src="js/FAQ.js"></script>
</body>
</html>